DataList.LocalizeJP: お出かけの準備、できたよぉ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Preparations to go out, complete!

DataList.LocalizeJP: らじゃー！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Roger!

DataList.LocalizeJP: ん？先生も一口いる？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Hmm? You want a bite, Sensei?

DataList.LocalizeJP: うぇー！どうして？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Eeeh! Why?

DataList.LocalizeJP: ひどーい！ご飯を我慢して頑張ったのにー。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I did my best to skip meals for this! You're the worst!

DataList.LocalizeJP: みんなで夏のグルメ巡りにしゅっぱーつ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Let's all go on a summer gourmet tour!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 海の家まで、もうすぐのはず！
DataList.LocalizeEN: The beach house should be right there!

DataList.LocalizeJP: うーん！終わったぁ。じゃ！とびっきり辛いかき氷でも食べに行こっ、先生！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Yay, it's over! Sensei, let's go get an extra spicy shaved ice!

DataList.LocalizeJP: よし、これで終わりだよね。じゃあ早くレモン焼きそば食べに行かないとっ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Mission's over, right? Now, let's go get a lemon yakisoba, quick!

DataList.LocalizeJP: よーし、力が湧いてきた！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Hooo, I'm feeling stronger!

DataList.LocalizeJP: いっくよー！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Here I go!.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 危ない危ない。
DataList.LocalizeEN: That was close.

DataList.LocalizeJP: いたっ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Ouch!

DataList.LocalizeJP: やめてー。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Stop!

DataList.LocalizeJP: ひ、ひどーい。
DataList.LocalizeEN: You're so mean!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 無駄無駄！
DataList.LocalizeEN: That's not going to work!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 暑いし、お腹も空いたけど、食事の前の運動は大事！
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's hot and I'm hungry, but it's important to exercise before eating.

DataList.LocalizeJP: ご飯の前にパッパッと終わらせよう！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Let's get this done before dinner!

DataList.LocalizeJP: まだいるの～？お腹すいた～。
DataList.LocalizeEN: There are still more? But I'm hungry!

DataList.LocalizeJP: ちゃちゃっと片付けて、なにか冷たい飲み物でも買いに行こっ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Let's clean up and go buy some cold drinks.

DataList.LocalizeJP: やる気マーックス！でも、そろそろお腹空いた……。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Motivation at max! I'm hungry already...

DataList.LocalizeJP: まだまだいろんなグルメを味わいたかったのにー。
DataList.LocalizeEN: But I wanted to try more gourmet...

DataList.LocalizeJP: こっちに行こう！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Let's go there!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 夏の美食を巡る旅は、まだまだこれからだよっ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: The trip of summer gastronomy has only just begun.

DataList.LocalizeJP: よし！じゃあ早く海の家に行こっ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Good! Now, let's go to the beach house, quick!

DataList.LocalizeJP: どれにしようかな？うん、これ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Which one, which one? Yup, this one!

DataList.LocalizeJP: う～ん、悩む。よし、これにしよっと！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Don't worry, let's do this

DataList.LocalizeJP: ジュース♪ジュース♪よーし！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Juice♪ Juice♪ Alright!

DataList.LocalizeJP: んっ…んっ…ぷはぁ！
じゅるっ、うん！冷えてる！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sip... Yup, it's freezing!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 美味しい！ごちそうさま！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Yum! Thanks for the meal!

DataList.LocalizeJP: どんな感じって？う～んとね～……美味しかったよ？チョコ味のウナギと同じくらい！
DataList.LocalizeEN: How does it taste? Well... It tasted good? About as good as chocolate eel!

DataList.LocalizeJP: ふう、お腹いっぱ～い！ありがとう、先生！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Phew, I'm full! Thank you, Sensei!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生、ごちそうさま！今度はまた一緒に冷やし中華でも食べに行こう！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Thank you for the meal, Sensei! Let's have chilled Chinese noodles again together sometime!

DataList.LocalizeJP: わあ、先生がくれたこれ、すっごく美味しい！え、食べ物じゃない？まあまあ、美味しかったからオッケーってことで！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Wow! This thing Sensei gave me was super yummy! Eh? It's not food? It's fine, as long as it's delicious!

DataList.LocalizeJP: やっぱり先生と一緒にいると楽しいな！
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's always fun when I'm with Sensei!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 二人でこれ食べよ、先生！くっついてると余計に暑いけど、でもやっぱり一緒に食べたいし！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sensei, let's eat this, the two of us! I know it's even hotter when we get too close together, but I still want to have this with you!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生、私ちょっとヘンかも……ドキドキが止まらなくて……熱中症かなぁ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sensei, I feel a little strange... my heart won't stop pounding... maybe a heat stroke?

DataList.LocalizeJP: 先生と一緒なら、今年の夏こそ食べたいもの全部制覇できるかも。行こう、先生！
DataList.LocalizeEN: If I'm with you, I might be able to conquer all the foods I want to eat this summer. Let's go, Sensei!
